Entities:
---------

** Channel
  * Description:
    - collection of channels

  * Attributes:
    - id
    - label
    - categories
    - countries
    - languages

  * Associations:
    - has-many categories
    - has-many countries
    - has-many languages

** Advert
   * Description:
     - collection of Ads

   * attributes:
     - id
     - label
     - categories
     - countries
     - languages
     - global-view-limit
     - constraint / rule

  * Associations:
    - has-many categories
    - has-many countries
    - has-many languages
    - has-one rule

** Category
   * Description:
     - collection of categories
     - tree structure and hence can represent hierarchies

   * Attributes:
     - id
     - label
     - parent

   * Associations
     - has-many-and-belongs-to advert
     - has-many-and-belongs-to channel

** Country
   * Description:
     - collection of countries

   * Attributes
     - label

   * Associations
     - has-many-and-belongs-to advert
     - has-many-and-belongs-to channel

** Language
   * Description:
     - collection of languages

   * Attributes
     - label

  * Associations:
    - has-many-and-belongs-to advert
    - has-many-and-belongs-to channel


** AdChannelLimit
   * Description:
     - collection of ad-to-channel view limit

   * Attributes
     - advert-id
     - channel-id
     - view-limit
     - view-counter

  * Associations:
    - belongs-to advert
    - belongs-to channel


** AdCountryLimit
   * Description:
     - collection of ad-to-country view limit

   * Attributes
     - advert-id
     - country-id
     - view-limit
     - view-counter

  * Associations:
    - belongs-to advert
    - belongs-to country
